data.description: This charming two story home is located in the heart of north east, close to parks, schools, shopping, and minutes away from Fort Bliss.  As you walk in the house you will be greeted by the brightness of the living room, the warmth of the beautiful wood floors, and the inviting welcoming fireplace. The kitchen has ample cabinet space and a cozy breakfast area, the layout of the kitchen and breakfast area flow harmoniously. The master bedroom is located downstairs for privacy and convenience. On the second floor you will find a bright loft, full bathroom and two additional bedrooms. The house enjoys of a large landscaped backyard and a professionally landscaped front yard that adds exquisite curb appeal.  This lovely home is a MUST SEE!
